four, five, six tracks,

00:32:21.030 --> 00:32:24.940
so that on any given night, if
someone's in, someone's out,

00:32:24.940 --> 00:32:27.850
this person can go
into this track.

00:32:27.850 --> 00:32:29.600
If he's out, I go
into his track,

00:32:29.600 --> 00:32:30.974
another guy goes into my track.

00:32:30.974 --> 00:32:32.390
So that's the
meaning of the word.

00:32:32.390 --> 00:32:33.400
MAX VON ESSEN: Is that
