00:46:17.610 --> 00:46:19.930
Maybe I will take a trip
up to Lincoln Center.

00:46:19.930 --> 00:46:24.570
And vice versa, because I think
maybe a ballet fan wouldn't

00:46:24.570 --> 00:46:26.800
necessarily come
and see a musical,

00:46:26.800 --> 00:46:29.570
because they might
think it's not for them.

00:46:29.570 --> 00:46:31.930
But then, knowing that
it's Christopher Wheeldon

00:46:31.930 --> 00:46:34.260
choreography, they'll
come down to see the show,

00:46:34.260 --> 00:46:36.051
and then they'll want
to see more musicals.

00:46:36.051 --> 00:46:38.410
So I think it works
both ways, actually.

00:46:38.410 --> 00:46:40.807
I'm hoping it will.

